e\nconnectivity, performed the best overall with respect to approximation ratios\nand chain break frequencies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 8 Jan 2023 10:02:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Jan 2023 21:36:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 20 Apr 2023 03:12:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-21"}
